00:28:28.810 --> 00:28:31.640
I think, at this point, we've
got it pretty much solved.

00:28:31.640 --> 00:28:36.200
We divide everything
by C g, flip it over,

00:28:36.200 --> 00:28:37.700
and you end up
with-- actually, I've

00:28:37.700 --> 00:28:40.130
already written out
the expression, which

00:28:40.130 --> 00:28:41.360
I want to show you guys here.

00:28:44.350 --> 00:28:47.620
Back to smoke shop
counting time.

00:28:47.620 --> 00:28:50.110
So I want to show you
