00:41:03.510 --> 00:41:08.968
mean that you can only have a
maximum of half of the sphere?

00:41:08.968 --> 00:41:10.260
MICHAEL SHORT: Not necessarily.

00:41:10.260 --> 00:41:12.010
Let's say you were to
encase your detector

00:41:12.010 --> 00:41:14.910
