00:53:08.500 --> 00:53:10.090
187, that's the half-life--

00:53:10.090 --> 00:53:12.130
23.9 hours.

00:53:12.130 --> 00:53:13.800
So with all of that--

00:53:13.800 --> 00:53:16.690
oh, and underneath
