00:53:16.690 --> 00:53:19.090
got what the gammas are--

00:53:19.090 --> 00:53:21.867
685, 479.

00:53:21.867 --> 00:53:23.200
it's got a whole mess of gammas.

00:53:23.200 --> 00:53:25.570
So that's a bunch of the
